		<div class="title">
			<h4><a id="comment_link_64550273" name="comment_link_64550273" href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23357471&amp;cid=64550273" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64550273)" >Ah yes, because sudo has a stellar track record</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64550273" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64550273); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>2</a>, Informative)</span></h4>
